<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<EAPIdentityProviderList xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="eap-metadata.xsd">
  <EAPIdentityProvider version="1" lang="en" ID="isu.edu.tw" namespace="urn:RFC4282:realm">
    <AuthenticationMethods>
      <AuthenticationMethod>
        <EAPMethod>
          <Type>25</Type>
        </EAPMethod>
        <ServerSideCredential>
          <CA format="X.509" encoding="base64"></CA>
          <ServerID>ISU-ISE.isu.edu.tw</ServerID>
        </ServerSideCredential>
        <ClientSideCredential>
          <OuterIdentity>isuwireless@isu.edu.tw</OuterIdentity>
          <InnerIdentitySuffix>isu.edu.tw</InnerIdentitySuffix>
          <InnerIdentityHint>true</InnerIdentityHint>
        </ClientSideCredential>
        <InnerAuthenticationMethod>
          <EAPMethod>
            <Type>26</Type>
          </EAPMethod>
        </InnerAuthenticationMethod>
      </AuthenticationMethod>
    </AuthenticationMethods>
    <CredentialApplicability>
      <IEEE80211>
        <SSID>eduroam</SSID>
        <MinRSNProto>CCMP</MinRSNProto>
      </IEEE80211>
      <IEEE80211>
        <SSID>ISU-secure</SSID>
        <MinRSNProto>CCMP</MinRSNProto>
      </IEEE80211>
      <IEEE80211>
        <ConsortiumOID>001bc50460</ConsortiumOID>
      </IEEE80211>
    </CredentialApplicability>
    <ProviderInfo>
      <DisplayName>I-SHOU University (ISU) [Maintained by eduroam TW Third-party Database]</DisplayName>
      <Description>請使用您學校提供的帳號與密碼登入。

本設定檔由學網漫遊第三方資料庫維護，並由臺灣學術無線網路漫遊中心監督管理。
若您確認帳號密碼正確仍無法連線，請聯絡 eduroamtw@googlegroups.com
 或 roamingcenter@gms.ndhu.edu.tw
。

如需進一步了解本計畫，請參閱：https://edur.isli.me/

Please log in using the account and password provided by your institution.

This configuration file is maintained by the "eduroam TW Third-party Database" and is supervised by the TANet Roaming Center.
If you are unable to connect despite entering the correct credentials, please contact eduroamtw@googlegroups.com
 or roamingcenter@gms.ndhu.edu.tw
.

For more information about this project, please visit: https://edur.isli.me/

Source: https://olis.isu.edu.tw/page/%E6%A0%A1%E5%9C%92%E7%B6%B2%E8%B7%AF-QElzyyeTd89Z</Description>
      <ProviderLocation>
        <Longitude>120.4069218</Longitude>
        <Latitude>22.7259477</Latitude>
      </ProviderLocation>
      <ProviderLogo mime="image/webp" encoding="base64"></ProviderLogo>
      <Helpdesk/>
    </ProviderInfo>
  </EAPIdentityProvider>
</EAPIdentityProviderList>
